Koh chhin-chhiuN7 cha2 u7 chit8-e5 lang5 in-ui7 tham-sim chiu7 thau-theh8 i e5 peng5-iu2 e5 chiN5.  Bo5 phah-sng3 hou7 i hoat-kian3 tioh8, chiu7 hou7 peng5-iu2 liah8 tiau5-teh, soa3 ka7 i hoah-chhat8.  Chit si5 hit e5 lang5 chin kiaN, kiaN-liau2 lang5 ui5-oa2--lai5, sou2-i2 chiu7 tui3 seng-khu thiu-chhut sio2-to lai5 ti2-khong3, ko2-jian5 tuh-si2 i e5 peng5-iu2. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 piN3-chiaN5 bou5-chai5 hai7-beng7 e5 choe7.  Khi2-thau5 si7 tham-sim, chiu7 piN3 choe3 bou5-chai5, soa3 hai7-beng7, tui3 an2-ni i chiu7 to5-chau2, soa3 piN3-choe3 kok-ka e5 to5-hoan7. Au7-lai5 keng3-jian5 ka-jip8 thou2-hui2 thoan5-the2, soa3 cho3-chhut thai5-lang5, pang3-hoe2, kan-im5, chhiuN2-toat8, kau3-boe2 tui7-loh8 kau3 be7 tit siu-sip8 e5 te7-pou7.
Khah-siong5 lang5 e5 hoan7-choe7 long2-si7 an2-ni, khi2-thau5 sio2-khoa2 au7-lai5 choe7 siN choe7, choe7 siong7 ka choe7, kau3-boe2 chiu7 kau3 ti7 put-kho2 siu-sip8 e5 te7-pou7.
